<div class="calcpad-output">
 <!-- HP variant of the creational helpers: $matrix$, $identity$, $diagonal$, banded, random and Vandermonde constructors emitting packed storage. -->
 <style>em {font-family:"Times New Roman";}</style>
 <p>
